<li id="cite_note-26"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26" title="">^</a></b> Studies mostly agree that antiseptic mouthwashes can help prevent recurrences:<br />
* <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMeiller_TF.2C_Kutcher_MJ.2C_Overholser_CD.2C_Niehaus_C.2C_DePaola_LG.2C_Siegel_MA1991">Meiller TF, Kutcher MJ, Overholser CD, Niehaus C, DePaola LG, Siegel MA (1991). "Effect of an antimicrobial mouthrinse on recurrent aphthous ulcerations". <i>Oral Surg. Oral Med. Oral Pathol.</i> <b>72</b> (4): 425–9. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2F0030-4220%2891%2990553-O" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2F0030-4220%2891%2990553-O" rel="nofollow">10.1016/0030-4220(91)90553-O</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1923440" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/1923440">PMID 1923440</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Effect+of+an+antimicrobial+mouthrinse+on+recurrent+aphthous+ulcerations&amp;rft.jtitle=Oral+Surg.+Oral+Med.+Oral+Pathol.&amp;rft.aulast=Meiller+TF%2C+Kutcher+MJ%2C+Overholser+CD%2C+Niehaus+C%2C+DePaola+LG%2C+Siegel+MA&amp;rft.au=Meiller+TF%2C+Kutcher+MJ%2C+Overholser+CD%2C+Niehaus+C%2C+DePaola+LG%2C+Siegel+MA&amp;rft.date=1991&amp;rft.volume=72&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=425%E2%80%939&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1016%2F0030-4220%2891%2990553-O&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/1923440&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span><br />
* <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFSkaare_AB.2C_Herlofson_BB.2C_Barkvoll_P1996">Skaare AB, Herlofson BB, Barkvoll P (1996). "Mouthrinses containing triclosan reduce the incidence of recurrent aphthous ulcers (RAU)". <i>J. Clin. Periodontol.</i> <b>23</b> (8): 778–81. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1600-051X.1996.tb00609.x" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1600-051X.1996.tb00609.x" rel="nofollow">10.1111/j.1600-051X.1996.tb00609.x</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/8877665" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/8877665">PMID 8877665</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Mouthrinses+containing+triclosan+reduce+the+incidence+of+recurrent+aphthous+ulcers+%28RAU%29&amp;rft.jtitle=J.+Clin.+Periodontol.&amp;rft.aulast=Skaare+AB%2C+Herlofson+BB%2C+Barkvoll+P&amp;rft.au=Skaare+AB%2C+Herlofson+BB%2C+Barkvoll+P&amp;rft.date=1996&amp;rft.volume=23&amp;rft.issue=8&amp;rft.pages=778%E2%80%9381&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1111%2Fj.1600-051X.1996.tb00609.x&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/8877665&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span><br />
But this is not accepted by all reports:<br />
* <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBarrons_RW2001">Barrons RW (2001). "Treatment strategies for recurrent oral aphthous ulcers". <i>Am J Health Syst Pharm</i> <b>58</b> (1): 41–50; quiz 51–3. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11194135" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11194135">PMID 11194135</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Treatment+strategies+for+recurrent+oral+aphthous+ulcers&amp;rft.jtitle=Am+J+Health+Syst+Pharm&amp;rft.aulast=Barrons+RW&amp;rft.au=Barrons+RW&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.volume=58&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=41%E2%80%9350%3B+quiz+51%E2%80%933&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/11194135&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-pmid8811135-27"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid8811135_27-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFHerlofson_BB.2C_Barkvoll_P1996">Herlofson BB, Barkvoll P (1996). "The effect of two toothpaste detergents on the frequency of recurrent aphthous ulcers". <i>Acta Odontol. Scand.</i> <b>54</b> (3): 150–3. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.3109%2F00016359609003515" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.3109%2F00016359609003515" rel="nofollow">10.3109/00016359609003515</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/8811135" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/8811135">PMID 8811135</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+effect+of+two+toothpaste+detergents+on+the+frequency+of+recurrent+aphthous+ulcers&amp;rft.jtitle=Acta+Odontol.+Scand.&amp;rft.aulast=Herlofson+BB%2C+Barkvoll+P&amp;rft.au=Herlofson+BB%2C+Barkvoll+P&amp;rft.date=1996&amp;rft.volume=54&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=150%E2%80%933&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.3109%2F00016359609003515&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/8811135&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-pmid9656847-28"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid9656847_28-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFChahine_L.2C_Sempson_N.2C_Wagoner_C1997">Chahine L, Sempson N, Wagoner C (1997). "The effect of sodium lauryl sulfate on recurrent aphthous ulcers: a clinical study". <i>Compend Contin Educ Dent</i> <b>18</b> (12): 1238–40. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9656847" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9656847">PMID 9656847</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+effect+of+sodium+lauryl+sulfate+on+recurrent+aphthous+ulcers%3A+a+clinical+study&amp;rft.jtitle=Compend+Contin+Educ+Dent&amp;rft.aulast=Chahine+L%2C+Sempson+N%2C+Wagoner+C&amp;rft.au=Chahine+L%2C+Sempson+N%2C+Wagoner+C&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft.volume=18&amp;rft.issue=12&amp;rft.pages=1238%E2%80%9340&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/9656847&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-pmid10218040-29"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid10218040_29-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFHealy_CM.2C_Paterson_M.2C_Joyston-Bechal_S.2C_Williams_DM.2C_Thornhill_MH1999">Healy CM, Paterson M, Joyston-Bechal S, Williams DM, Thornhill MH (1999). "The effect of a sodium lauryl sulfate-free dentifrice on patients with recurrent oral ulceration". <i>Oral Dis</i> <b>5</b> (1): 39–43. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10218040" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10218040">PMID 10218040</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+effect+of+a+sodium+lauryl+sulfate-free+dentifrice+on+patients+with+recurrent+oral+ulceration&amp;rft.jtitle=Oral+Dis&amp;rft.aulast=Healy+CM%2C+Paterson+M%2C+Joyston-Bechal+S%2C+Williams+DM%2C+Thornhill+MH&amp;rft.au=Healy+CM%2C+Paterson+M%2C+Joyston-Bechal+S%2C+Williams+DM%2C+Thornhill+MH&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=39%E2%80%9343&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/10218040&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-pmid3467416-30"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid3467416_30-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWang_SW.2C_Li_HK.2C_He_JS.2C_Yin_TA1986">Wang SW, Li HK, He JS, Yin TA (1986). "[The trace element zinc and aphthosis. The determination of plasma zinc and the treatment of aphthosis with zinc]" (in French). <i>Rev Stomatol Chir Maxillofac</i> <b>87</b> (5): 339–43. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/3467416" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/3467416">PMID 3467416</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=%5BThe+trace+element+zinc+and+aphthosis.+The+determination+of+plasma+zinc+and+the+treatment+of+aphthosis+with+zinc%5D&amp;rft.jtitle=Rev+Stomatol+Chir+Maxillofac&amp;rft.aulast=Wang+SW%2C+Li+HK%2C+He+JS%2C+Yin+TA&amp;rft.au=Wang+SW%2C+Li+HK%2C+He+JS%2C+Yin+TA&amp;rft.date=1986&amp;rft.volume=87&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.pages=339%E2%80%9343&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/3467416&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-pmid12790293-31"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid12790293_31-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFOrbak_R.2C_Cicek_Y.2C_Tezel_A.2C_Dogru_Y2003">Orbak R, Cicek Y, Tezel A, Dogru Y (2003). "Effects of zinc treatment in patients with recurrent aphthous stomatitis". <i>Dent Mater J</i> <b>22</b> (1): 21–9. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12790293" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12790293">PMID 12790293</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Effects+of+zinc+treatment+in+patients+with+recurrent+aphthous+stomatitis&amp;rft.jtitle=Dent+Mater+J&amp;rft.aulast=Orbak+R%2C+Cicek+Y%2C+Tezel+A%2C+Dogru+Y&amp;rft.au=Orbak+R%2C+Cicek+Y%2C+Tezel+A%2C+Dogru+Y&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.volume=22&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=21%E2%80%939&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/12790293&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-pmid7048184-32"><b><a href="#cite_ref-pmid7048184_32-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWray_D1982">Wray D (1982). "A double-blind trial of systemic zinc sulfate in recurrent aphthous stomatitis". <i>Oral Surg. Oral Med. Oral Pathol.</i> <b>53</b> (5): 469–72. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2F0030-4220%2882%2990459-5" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016%2F0030-4220%2882%2990459-5" rel="nofollow">10.1016/0030-4220(82)90459-5</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/7048184" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/7048184">PMID 7048184</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=A+double-blind+trial+of+systemic+zinc+sulfate+in+recurrent+aphthous+stomatitis&amp;rft.jtitle=Oral+Surg.+Oral+Med.+Oral+Pathol.&amp;rft.aulast=Wray+D&amp;rft.au=Wray+D&amp;rft.date=1982&amp;rft.volume=53&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.pages=469%E2%80%9372&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1016%2F0030-4220%2882%2990459-5&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/7048184&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Aphthous_ulcer"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
